longBusinessSummary: BeammWave AB (publ) provides single radio chips with fully integrated antennas in Sweden. Its products are used in various applications, including phones, fixed wireless CPE's, and base stations. BeammWave AB (publ) was founded in 2017 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
